    * url baseUrl
    * call read(login) consortiaAdmin
    * configure headers = { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'x-okapi-token': '#(okapitoken)', 'x-okapi-tenant': '#(centralTenant)', 'Accept': 'application/json' }
    * configure retry = { count: 30, interval: 10000 }

